{"tid":665771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WSJ：Google 已停止提供 Android 安全性更新給中興通訊","createTime":"2018-05-15T09:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T09:17:50.000Z","uid":150685,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"41b6b9711f7d2b2402ba0e03defd1c28ab0f896c","tid":665771,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:00:14.000Z","msg":"澳洲最大電信商 Telstra Corp. 5 月 10 日表示，已停售由中興通訊所代工的自有品牌智慧型手機。華爾街日報（WSJ）5 月 14 日引述知情人士報導，Google 已遵照美國商務部的命令停止提供技術支援以 及Android 作業系統安全性更新 / 功能更新給中興通訊。報導指出，這意味著部分消費者的中興智慧型手機將變得無法正常使用。Canalys 分析師 Mo Jia 指出，使用者個人資料的安全性可能不足，用戶也將無法體驗最新功能。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2018/05/15/wsj-google-android-zte/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2018%2F05%2F15%2Fwsj-google-android-zte%2F&d=BRltTxiy%2FjBf63PtM8VK2HIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=399fc57f\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2018/05/15/wsj-google-android-zte/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2afa9d978dac8db251be40356073c0155caee428","tid":665771,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:01:16.000Z","msg":"又講一套 做一套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"214f0b9dc4a60c4620c5e266928a6057f05e776b","tid":665771,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:03:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60ae0d40cf423ff0582fdadd1134571a727731b9","tid":665771,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a3ec12a56c097923d589f5a42d6604207828c12","tid":665771,"uid":2772,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T